    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris Iesu Christi, Nos <persName ref="#people/90"
                            key="#Princeps #Patricius">Vvaimarius</persName> in Dei nomine <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, et <rs key="#Patricius">imperialis
                            Patricio</rs> et <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/298"
                            >Quaimarius</persName> divina previdentia <rs key="#Princeps"
                            >Langobardorum gentis princeps</rs>, motus Dei omnipotentis
                        misericordia, quam et pro remedium animae mee et ex gentis nostrae
                        salvationem atque <rs key="#Intercessory">per rogum et postulationem</rs>
                        <persName key="#Society"><name ref="Rainfredus">Ragemfrid</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Society">medico</rs> et <persName key="#Priests"><name
                                ref="Ermenaldus">Ermenaldi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbyteri</rs> oratori nostro, concessimus in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/84" key="#Monasteries">S.
                            Benedicti</orgName>, ubi nunc, Deo favente, modo domnus <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/195">Leo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">Abbas</rs> preesse, integra <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs>
                        illam de <rs key="#Other_administrative_unit">locus</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Villages/settlements #Curtes #Other_administrative_unit"
                            ref="#places/540">Rota</placeName>, qui fuit <persName key="#Marriages"
                                ><name ref="Adalferius">Adelferius</name>
                            <name ref="Rofredus">Roffrid</name></persName>, quod ad vivendum
                        reliquit <persName key="#Marriages #auntOf"><name ref="Rodelchisa"
                                >Rodelchisae</name></persName>, qui fuit <rs key="#Marriages"
                            >uxor</rs> eius, defuncta tum ipsa Rodelchisa, omnia illius rebus et
                        facultatibus <rs key="#Law">per gradum subcessionis legibus</rs>, obvenit
                            <persName key="#sonOf #nephewOf"><name ref="Rotarius"
                            >Roderis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#sonOf">filius</rs>
                        <persName key="#fatherOf"><name ref="Gaido">Gaidoni</name></persName>, qui
                        fuit <rs key="#nephewOf">nepotes</rs> ipsius Rodelchisae, omnia tum rebus
                        substanciam ipsius Roderis<rs key="#Law"> legibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fiscal_property #Confiscation">ad sacrum nostrum Palatium pervenit
                            potestatem</rs>, pro eo quod in consilio mortis nostrae consiliatus
                        fuit. Deinde pro nostrae salutis animae predicta <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Wine #Chestnuts #Acorns #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Personal_statuses"
                            ref="#estates/242">curte de Rota</geogName> cum <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis</rs>, et sedimen suam et
                        territoriae <rs key="#Production">arbusta</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Chestnuts">castanieta</rs>, <rs key="#Acorns">quertii</rs>, et
                        a monte quam et in plano, cum viis et aquis, cum <rs
                            key="#Slave_labour #Personal_statuses #Slave">servis et ancillis</rs> et
                        cum omnia ex ipsa curte pertinentibus, qualiter ipsa nominata Rodelchisa eas
                        tenuit vel dominavit, sic totum in integrum in prefato suprascripto
                        monasterio pro nostrae salutis animae offeruimus, in eam videlicet racionem,
                        ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum <rs
                            key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma">præceptum</rs> ea quae prelegitur
                        prefato suprascripto monasterio et eius abbatibus vel rectores securiter et
                        firmiter possideant, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus,
                        gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus partibus ipsius monasterii abeant
                        aliqua molestia aut requisitionem, sed in perpetuis temporibus firmiter
                        habere et possidere valeatis. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex iussonem
                        superscriptae potestatis et per eorum demandationem quod scripsi ego
                            <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Ursus">Ursus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/84"
                            key="#Cities">Salerno</placeName> de anno vicesimo quarto et octavo anno
                        ipsorum principibus, mense Augustus, tertia indictione. </ab>
